 static String strEscape(String s,char quote,String doublequoteEscape,String singlequoteEscape,String backslashEscape,CharsetEncoder outputCharsetEncoder){
 StringBuilder sb=new StringBuilder(s.length()+2);
 sb.append(quote);
 for(int i=0;i<s.length();i++){
 char c=s.charAt(i);
 switch (c){
 case '\n' :
 
 sb.append("\\n");
 break;
 case '\r' :
 
 sb.append("\\r");
 break;
 case '\t' :
 
 sb.append("\\t");
 break;
 case '\\' :
 
 sb.append(backslashEscape);
 break;
 case '\"' :
 
 sb.append(doublequoteEscape);
 break;
 case '\'' :
 
 sb.append(singlequoteEscape);
 break;
 case '>' :
 
 if(i>=2&&((s.charAt(i-1)=='-'&&s.charAt(i-2)=='-')||(s.charAt(i-1)==']'&&s.charAt(i-2)==']'))){
 sb.append("\\>");
 }else {
 sb.append(c);
 }
 break;
 case '<' :
 
  final String END_SCRIPT="/script";
  final String START_COMMENT="!--";
 if(s.regionMatches(true,i+1,END_SCRIPT,0,END_SCRIPT.length())){
 sb.append("<\\");
 }else {
 if(s.regionMatches(false,i+1,START_COMMENT,0,START_COMMENT.length())){
 sb.append("<\\");
 }else {
 sb.append(c);
 }
 }
 break;
 default :
 
 if(outputCharsetEncoder!=null){
 if(outputCharsetEncoder.canEncode(c)){
 sb.append(c);
 }else {
 appendHexJavaScriptRepresentation(sb,c);
 }
 }else {
 if(c>0x1f&&c<=0x7f){
 sb.append(c);
+continue;
 }else {
 appendHexJavaScriptRepresentation(sb,c);
 }
 }
 }
 }
 sb.append(quote);
 return sb.toString();
 }

 if(s.regionMatches(true,i+1,END_SCRIPT,0,END_SCRIPT.length())){
 sb.append("<\\");
 }else {
 if(s.regionMatches(false,i+1,START_COMMENT,0,START_COMMENT.length())){
 sb.append("<\\");
 }else {
 sb.append(c);
 }
 }
 break;
 default :
 
 if(outputCharsetEncoder!=null){
 if(outputCharsetEncoder.canEncode(c)){
 sb.append(c);
 }else {
 appendHexJavaScriptRepresentation(sb,c);
 }
+i++;
 }else {
 if(c>0x1f&&c<=0x7f){
 sb.append(c);
 }else {
 appendHexJavaScriptRepresentation(sb,c);
 }
 }
 }
 }
 sb.append(quote);
 return sb.toString();

 static String strEscape(String s,char quote,String doublequoteEscape,String singlequoteEscape,String backslashEscape,CharsetEncoder outputCharsetEncoder){
 StringBuilder sb=new StringBuilder(s.length()+2);
 sb.append(quote);
 for(int i=0;i<s.length();i++){
 char c=s.charAt(i);
 switch (c){
 case '\n' :
 
 sb.append("\\n");
 break;
 case '\r' :
 
 sb.append("\\r");
 break;
 case '\t' :
 
 sb.append("\\t");
 break;
 case '\\' :
 
 sb.append(backslashEscape);
 break;
 case '\"' :
 
 sb.append(doublequoteEscape);
 break;
 case '\'' :
 
 sb.append(singlequoteEscape);
 break;
 case '>' :
 
 if(i>=2&&((s.charAt(i-1)=='-'&&s.charAt(i-2)=='-')||(s.charAt(i-1)==']'&&s.charAt(i-2)==']'))){
 sb.append("\\>");
 }else {
 sb.append(c);
 }
 break;
 case '<' :
 
  final String END_SCRIPT="/script";
  final String START_COMMENT="!--";
 if(s.regionMatches(true,i+1,END_SCRIPT,0,END_SCRIPT.length())){
 sb.append("<\\");
 }else {
 if(s.regionMatches(false,i+1,START_COMMENT,0,START_COMMENT.length())){
 sb.append("<\\");
 }else {
 sb.append(c);
 }
 }
 break;
 default :
 
 if(outputCharsetEncoder!=null){
 if(outputCharsetEncoder.canEncode(c)){
 sb.append(c);
 }else {
 appendHexJavaScriptRepresentation(sb,c);
 }
 }else {
 if(c>0x1f&&c<=0x7f){
 sb.append(c);
+return null;
 }else {
 appendHexJavaScriptRepresentation(sb,c);
+return null;
 }
 }
 }
 }
 sb.append(quote);
 return sb.toString();

 sb.append("\\r");
 break;

+sb.append(("\\t").toLowerCase());

 break;

 sb.append(singlequoteEscape);

 sb.append("\\>");
 }else {
 sb.append(c);
 }
 break;
 case '<' :
 
  final String END_SCRIPT="/script";
  final String START_COMMENT="!--";
 if(s.regionMatches(true,i+1,END_SCRIPT,0,END_SCRIPT.length())){
 sb.append("<\\");
 }else {
 if(s.regionMatches(false,i+1,START_COMMENT,0,START_COMMENT.length())){
 sb.append("<\\");
 }else {
 sb.append(c);
 }

  final String START_COMMENT="!--";

 sb.append("<\\");

 sb.append("<\\");
 }else {
 sb.append(c);

 }
 }else {

 }else {

 }
+break;
 }

 break;

 sb.append("\\t");
 break;
 case '\\' :
 
 sb.append(backslashEscape);

 sb.append(doublequoteEscape);
 break;
 case '\'' :
 
 sb.append(singlequoteEscape);

 sb.append("\\>");
 }else {
 sb.append(c);
 }
 break;
 case '<' :
 
  final String END_SCRIPT="/script";
  final String START_COMMENT="!--";
 if(s.regionMatches(true,i+1,END_SCRIPT,0,END_SCRIPT.length())){
 sb.append("<\\");
 }else {
 if(s.regionMatches(false,i+1,START_COMMENT,0,START_COMMENT.length())){
 sb.append("<\\");
 }else {
 sb.append(c);
 }
 }
 break;

 static String strEscape(String s,char quote,String doublequoteEscape,String singlequoteEscape,String backslashEscape,CharsetEncoder outputCharsetEncoder){

 sb.append(quote);
 for(int i=0;i<s.length();i++){
 char c=s.charAt(i);
 switch (c){
 case '\n' :
 
 sb.append("\\n");
 break;
 case '\r' :
 
 sb.append("\\r");
 break;
 case '\t' :
 
 sb.append("\\t");
 break;
 case '\\' :
 
 sb.append(backslashEscape);
 break;
 case '\"' :
 
 sb.append(doublequoteEscape);
 break;
 case '\'' :
 
 sb.append(singlequoteEscape);
 break;
 case '>' :

 sb.append("\\>");
 }else {
 sb.append(c);
 }
 break;
 case '<' :
 
  final String END_SCRIPT="/script";
  final String START_COMMENT="!--";
 if(s.regionMatches(true,i+1,END_SCRIPT,0,END_SCRIPT.length())){
 sb.append("<\\");
 }else {
 if(s.regionMatches(false,i+1,START_COMMENT,0,START_COMMENT.length())){
 sb.append("<\\");
 }else {
 sb.append(c);
 }
 }
 break;
 default :

 sb.append(quote);
 for(int i=0;i<s.length();i++){

 switch (c){
 case '\n' :
 
 sb.append("\\n");
 break;
 case '\r' :
 
 sb.append("\\r");
 break;
 case '\t' :
 
 sb.append("\\t");

 break;
 case '\'' :
 
 sb.append(singlequoteEscape);

 sb.append("\\>");

  final String END_SCRIPT="/script";
  final String START_COMMENT="!--";

 sb.append("<\\");
 }else {

 sb.append("<\\");
 }else {
 sb.append(c);
 }
 }
 break;

 static String strEscape(String s,char quote,String doublequoteEscape,String singlequoteEscape,String backslashEscape,CharsetEncoder outputCharsetEncoder){

 sb.append(quote);
 for(int i=0;i<s.length();i++){
 char c=s.charAt(i);
 switch (c){
 case '\n' :
 
 sb.append("\\n");
 break;
 case '\r' :
 
 sb.append("\\r");
 break;
 case '\t' :
 
 sb.append("\\t");
 break;
 case '\\' :
 
 sb.append(backslashEscape);
 break;
 case '\"' :
 
 sb.append(doublequoteEscape);
 break;
 case '\'' :
 
 sb.append(singlequoteEscape);
 break;
 case '>' :

 sb.append("\\>");
 }else {
 sb.append(c);
 }
 break;

  final String END_SCRIPT="/script";
  final String START_COMMENT="!--";
 if(s.regionMatches(true,i+1,END_SCRIPT,0,END_SCRIPT.length())){
 sb.append("<\\");
 }else {
 if(s.regionMatches(false,i+1,START_COMMENT,0,START_COMMENT.length())){
 sb.append("<\\");
 }else {
 sb.append(c);
 }
 }
 break;
 default :

 appendHexJavaScriptRepresentation(sb,c);

 static String strEscape(String s,char quote,String doublequoteEscape,String singlequoteEscape,String backslashEscape,CharsetEncoder outputCharsetEncoder){
 StringBuilder sb=new StringBuilder(s.length()+2);
 sb.append(quote);
 for(int i=0;i<s.length();i++){
 char c=s.charAt(i);
 switch (c){
 case '\n' :
 
 sb.append("\\n");
 break;
 case '\r' :
 
 sb.append("\\r");
 break;
 case '\t' :
 
 sb.append("\\t");
 break;
 case '\\' :
 
 sb.append(backslashEscape);
 break;
 case '\"' :
 
 sb.append(doublequoteEscape);
 break;
 case '\'' :
 
 sb.append(singlequoteEscape);
 break;
 case '>' :
 
 if(i>=2&&((s.charAt(i-1)=='-'&&s.charAt(i-2)=='-')||(s.charAt(i-1)==']'&&s.charAt(i-2)==']'))){
 sb.append("\\>");
 }else {
 sb.append(c);
 }
 break;
 case '<' :
 
  final String END_SCRIPT="/script";
  final String START_COMMENT="!--";
 if(s.regionMatches(true,i+1,END_SCRIPT,0,END_SCRIPT.length())){
 sb.append("<\\");
 }else {
 if(s.regionMatches(false,i+1,START_COMMENT,0,START_COMMENT.length())){
 sb.append("<\\");
 }else {
 sb.append(c);
 }
 }
 break;
 default :
 
 if(outputCharsetEncoder!=null){
 if(outputCharsetEncoder.canEncode(c)){
 sb.append(c);
 }else {
 appendHexJavaScriptRepresentation(sb,c);
 }
 }else {
+sb.append(c);
 if(c>0x1f&&c<=0x7f){
 sb.append(c);
 }else {
 appendHexJavaScriptRepresentation(sb,c);
 }
 }
 }
 }
 sb.append(quote);
 return sb.toString();
 }

 sb.append(backslashEscape);

 sb.append(doublequoteEscape);
 break;

 }else {
 sb.append(c);

 break;

  final String START_COMMENT="!--";

 sb.append("<\\");

 sb.append("<\\");

 sb.append(c);

 static String strEscape(String s,char quote,String doublequoteEscape,String singlequoteEscape,String backslashEscape,CharsetEncoder outputCharsetEncoder){
 StringBuilder sb=new StringBuilder(s.length()+2);
 sb.append(quote);
 for(int i=0;i<s.length();i++){
+assert (doublequoteEscape!=null);
 char c=s.charAt(i);
 switch (c){
 case '\n' :
 
 sb.append("\\n");
 break;
 case '\r' :
 
 sb.append("\\r");
 break;
 case '\t' :
 
 sb.append("\\t");
 break;
 case '\\' :
 
 sb.append(backslashEscape);
 break;
 case '\"' :
 
 sb.append(doublequoteEscape);
 break;
 case '\'' :
 
 sb.append(singlequoteEscape);
 break;
 case '>' :
 
 if(i>=2&&((s.charAt(i-1)=='-'&&s.charAt(i-2)=='-')||(s.charAt(i-1)==']'&&s.charAt(i-2)==']'))){
 sb.append("\\>");
 }else {
 sb.append(c);
 }
 break;
 case '<' :
 
  final String END_SCRIPT="/script";
  final String START_COMMENT="!--";
 if(s.regionMatches(true,i+1,END_SCRIPT,0,END_SCRIPT.length())){
 sb.append("<\\");
 }else {
 if(s.regionMatches(false,i+1,START_COMMENT,0,START_COMMENT.length())){
 sb.append("<\\");
 }else {
 sb.append(c);
 }
 }
 break;
 default :
 
 if(outputCharsetEncoder!=null){
 if(outputCharsetEncoder.canEncode(c)){
 sb.append(c);
 }else {
 appendHexJavaScriptRepresentation(sb,c);
 }
 }else {
 if(c>0x1f&&c<=0x7f){
 sb.append(c);
 }else {
 appendHexJavaScriptRepresentation(sb,c);
 }
 }
 }
 }
 sb.append(quote);
 return sb.toString();
 }

 sb.append(quote);
 for(int i=0;i<s.length();i++){
 char c=s.charAt(i);
 switch (c){
 case '\n' :
 
 sb.append("\\n");
 break;
 case '\r' :
 
 sb.append("\\r");
 break;
 case '\t' :
 
 sb.append("\\t");
 break;
 case '\\' :
 
 sb.append(backslashEscape);
 break;
 case '\"' :
 
 sb.append(doublequoteEscape);
 break;
 case '\'' :
 
 sb.append(singlequoteEscape);
 break;
 case '>' :
 
 if(i>=2&&((s.charAt(i-1)=='-'&&s.charAt(i-2)=='-')||(s.charAt(i-1)==']'&&s.charAt(i-2)==']'))){
 sb.append("\\>");
 }else {
 sb.append(c);
 }
 break;
 case '<' :
 
  final String END_SCRIPT="/script";
  final String START_COMMENT="!--";
 if(s.regionMatches(true,i+1,END_SCRIPT,0,END_SCRIPT.length())){
 sb.append("<\\");
 }else {
 if(s.regionMatches(false,i+1,START_COMMENT,0,START_COMMENT.length())){
 sb.append("<\\");
 }else {
 sb.append(c);
 }
 }
 break;
 default :
 
 if(outputCharsetEncoder!=null){
 if(outputCharsetEncoder.canEncode(c)){
 sb.append(c);
 }else {
 appendHexJavaScriptRepresentation(sb,c);
 }
 }else {
 if(c>0x1f&&c<=0x7f){
 sb.append(c);
+sb.append(quote);
 }else {
 appendHexJavaScriptRepresentation(sb,c);
 }
 }
 }
 }

 static String strEscape(String s,char quote,String doublequoteEscape,String singlequoteEscape,String backslashEscape,CharsetEncoder outputCharsetEncoder){
 StringBuilder sb=new StringBuilder(s.length()+2);
 sb.append(quote);
 for(int i=0;i<s.length();i++){
+if(s.equalsIgnoreCase("/")){
+return s;
+}
 char c=s.charAt(i);
 switch (c){
 case '\n' :
 
 sb.append("\\n");
 break;
 case '\r' :
 
 sb.append("\\r");
 break;
 case '\t' :
 
 sb.append("\\t");
 break;
 case '\\' :
 
 sb.append(backslashEscape);
 break;
 case '\"' :
 
 sb.append(doublequoteEscape);
 break;
 case '\'' :
 
 sb.append(singlequoteEscape);
 break;
 case '>' :
 
 if(i>=2&&((s.charAt(i-1)=='-'&&s.charAt(i-2)=='-')||(s.charAt(i-1)==']'&&s.charAt(i-2)==']'))){
 sb.append("\\>");
 }else {
 sb.append(c);
 }
 break;
 case '<' :
 
  final String END_SCRIPT="/script";
  final String START_COMMENT="!--";
 if(s.regionMatches(true,i+1,END_SCRIPT,0,END_SCRIPT.length())){
 sb.append("<\\");
 }else {
 if(s.regionMatches(false,i+1,START_COMMENT,0,START_COMMENT.length())){
 sb.append("<\\");
 }else {
 sb.append(c);
 }
 }
 break;
 default :
 
 if(outputCharsetEncoder!=null){
 if(outputCharsetEncoder.canEncode(c)){
 sb.append(c);
 }else {
 appendHexJavaScriptRepresentation(sb,c);
 }
 }else {
 if(c>0x1f&&c<=0x7f){
 sb.append(c);
 }else {
 appendHexJavaScriptRepresentation(sb,c);
 }
 }
 }
 }
 sb.append(quote);
 return sb.toString();

 static String strEscape(String s,char quote,String doublequoteEscape,String singlequoteEscape,String backslashEscape,CharsetEncoder outputCharsetEncoder){
 StringBuilder sb=new StringBuilder(s.length()+2);
 sb.append(quote);
 for(int i=0;i<s.length();i++){
 char c=s.charAt(i);
+assert (backslashEscape!=null);
 switch (c){
 case '\n' :
 
 sb.append("\\n");
 break;
 case '\r' :
 
 sb.append("\\r");
 break;
 case '\t' :
 
 sb.append("\\t");
 break;
 case '\\' :
 
 sb.append(backslashEscape);
 break;
 case '\"' :
 
 sb.append(doublequoteEscape);
 break;
 case '\'' :
 
 sb.append(singlequoteEscape);
 break;
 case '>' :
 
 if(i>=2&&((s.charAt(i-1)=='-'&&s.charAt(i-2)=='-')||(s.charAt(i-1)==']'&&s.charAt(i-2)==']'))){
 sb.append("\\>");
 }else {
 sb.append(c);
 }
 break;
 case '<' :
 
  final String END_SCRIPT="/script";
  final String START_COMMENT="!--";
 if(s.regionMatches(true,i+1,END_SCRIPT,0,END_SCRIPT.length())){
 sb.append("<\\");
 }else {
 if(s.regionMatches(false,i+1,START_COMMENT,0,START_COMMENT.length())){
 sb.append("<\\");
 }else {
 sb.append(c);
 }
 }
 break;
 default :
 
 if(outputCharsetEncoder!=null){
 if(outputCharsetEncoder.canEncode(c)){
 sb.append(c);
 }else {
 appendHexJavaScriptRepresentation(sb,c);
 }
 }else {
 if(c>0x1f&&c<=0x7f){
 sb.append(c);
 }else {
 appendHexJavaScriptRepresentation(sb,c);
 }
 }
 }
 }
 sb.append(quote);
 return sb.toString();
 }

 sb.append(quote);
 for(int i=0;i<s.length();i++){

 case '\n' :

 break;

  final String START_COMMENT="!--";

 sb.append("<\\");

 sb.append("<\\");

 }

 break;

 static String strEscape(String s,char quote,String doublequoteEscape,String singlequoteEscape,String backslashEscape,CharsetEncoder outputCharsetEncoder){

 sb.append(quote);
 for(int i=0;i<s.length();i++){
 char c=s.charAt(i);
 switch (c){
 case '\n' :
 
 sb.append("\\n");
 break;
 case '\r' :
 
 sb.append("\\r");
 break;
 case '\t' :
 
 sb.append("\\t");
 break;
 case '\\' :
 
 sb.append(backslashEscape);
 break;
 case '\"' :
 
 sb.append(doublequoteEscape);
 break;
 case '\'' :
 
 sb.append(singlequoteEscape);
 break;
 case '>' :
 
 if(i>=2&&((s.charAt(i-1)=='-'&&s.charAt(i-2)=='-')||(s.charAt(i-1)==']'&&s.charAt(i-2)==']'))){
 sb.append("\\>");
 }else {
 sb.append(c);
+JOptionPane.showMessageDialog(null,"No se pudo cargar la cancin","Error",JOptionPane.ERROR_MESSAGE);
 }
 break;
 case '<' :
 
  final String END_SCRIPT="/script";
  final String START_COMMENT="!--";
 if(s.regionMatches(true,i+1,END_SCRIPT,0,END_SCRIPT.length())){
 sb.append("<\\");
 }else {
 if(s.regionMatches(false,i+1,START_COMMENT,0,START_COMMENT.length())){
 sb.append("<\\");
 }else {
 sb.append(c);
 }
 }
 break;
 default :

 if(outputCharsetEncoder.canEncode(c)){
 sb.append(c);
 }else {
 appendHexJavaScriptRepresentation(sb,c);
 }
 }else {
 if(c>0x1f&&c<=0x7f){
 sb.append(c);
 }else {

 }
 }

 static String strEscape(String s,char quote,String doublequoteEscape,String singlequoteEscape,String backslashEscape,CharsetEncoder outputCharsetEncoder){

 sb.append(quote);
 for(int i=0;i<s.length();i++){
 char c=s.charAt(i);
 switch (c){
 case '\n' :
 
 sb.append("\\n");
 break;
 case '\r' :
 
 sb.append("\\r");
 break;
 case '\t' :

 break;

 break;
 case '\"' :

 break;
 case '\'' :
 
 sb.append(singlequoteEscape);
 break;
 case '>' :

 sb.append("\\>");
 }else {
 sb.append(c);
 }
 break;
 case '<' :
 
  final String END_SCRIPT="/script";
  final String START_COMMENT="!--";
 if(s.regionMatches(true,i+1,END_SCRIPT,0,END_SCRIPT.length())){
 sb.append("<\\");
 }else {
 if(s.regionMatches(false,i+1,START_COMMENT,0,START_COMMENT.length())){
 sb.append("<\\");
 }else {
 sb.append(c);
 }
 }
 break;
 default :

 sb.append(quote);
 for(int i=0;i<s.length();i++){
 char c=s.charAt(i);
 switch (c){
 case '\n' :
 
 sb.append("\\n");
 break;
 case '\r' :
 
 sb.append("\\r");
 break;
 case '\t' :
 
 sb.append("\\t");
 break;
 case '\\' :
 
 sb.append(backslashEscape);
 break;
 case '\"' :
 
 sb.append(doublequoteEscape);
 break;
 case '\'' :
 
 sb.append(singlequoteEscape);
 break;
 case '>' :
 
 if(i>=2&&((s.charAt(i-1)=='-'&&s.charAt(i-2)=='-')||(s.charAt(i-1)==']'&&s.charAt(i-2)==']'))){
 sb.append("\\>");
 }else {
 sb.append(c);
 }
 break;
 case '<' :
 
  final String END_SCRIPT="/script";
  final String START_COMMENT="!--";
 if(s.regionMatches(true,i+1,END_SCRIPT,0,END_SCRIPT.length())){
 sb.append("<\\");
 }else {
 if(s.regionMatches(false,i+1,START_COMMENT,0,START_COMMENT.length())){
 sb.append("<\\");
 }else {
 sb.append(c);
 }
 }
 break;
 default :
 
 if(outputCharsetEncoder!=null){
+if(outputCharsetEncoder==null){
+throw new IllegalStateException("player is not initialised, game might not be started");
+}
 if(outputCharsetEncoder.canEncode(c)){
 sb.append(c);
 }else {
 appendHexJavaScriptRepresentation(sb,c);
 }
 }else {
 if(c>0x1f&&c<=0x7f){
 sb.append(c);
 }else {
 appendHexJavaScriptRepresentation(sb,c);
 }
 }
 }
 }
 sb.append(quote);

 static String strEscape(String s,char quote,String doublequoteEscape,String singlequoteEscape,String backslashEscape,CharsetEncoder outputCharsetEncoder){
 StringBuilder sb=new StringBuilder(s.length()+2);
 sb.append(quote);
 for(int i=0;i<s.length();i++){
 char c=s.charAt(i);
 switch (c){
 case '\n' :
 
 sb.append("\\n");
 break;
 case '\r' :
 
 sb.append("\\r");
 break;
 case '\t' :
 
 sb.append("\\t");
 break;
 case '\\' :
 
 sb.append(backslashEscape);
 break;
 case '\"' :
 
 sb.append(doublequoteEscape);
 break;
 case '\'' :
 
 sb.append(singlequoteEscape);
 break;
 case '>' :
 
 if(i>=2&&((s.charAt(i-1)=='-'&&s.charAt(i-2)=='-')||(s.charAt(i-1)==']'&&s.charAt(i-2)==']'))){
 sb.append("\\>");
 }else {
 sb.append(c);
 }
 break;
 case '<' :
 
  final String END_SCRIPT="/script";
  final String START_COMMENT="!--";
 if(s.regionMatches(true,i+1,END_SCRIPT,0,END_SCRIPT.length())){
 sb.append("<\\");
 }else {
 if(s.regionMatches(false,i+1,START_COMMENT,0,START_COMMENT.length())){
 sb.append("<\\");
 }else {
 sb.append(c);
 }
 }
 break;
 default :
 
 if(outputCharsetEncoder!=null){
 if(outputCharsetEncoder.canEncode(c)){
 sb.append(c);
 }else {
 appendHexJavaScriptRepresentation(sb,c);
 }
 }else {
-if(c>0x1f&&c<=0x7f){
+if(c>0x1f&&c<=0x7f||"".equals(c>0x1f)){
 sb.append(c);
 }else {
 appendHexJavaScriptRepresentation(sb,c);
 }
 }
 }
 }
 sb.append(quote);
 return sb.toString();
 }

 static String strEscape(String s,char quote,String doublequoteEscape,String singlequoteEscape,String backslashEscape,CharsetEncoder outputCharsetEncoder){
 StringBuilder sb=new StringBuilder(s.length()+2);
 sb.append(quote);
 for(int i=0;i<s.length();i++){
 char c=s.charAt(i);
 switch (c){
 case '\n' :
 
 sb.append("\\n");
 break;
 case '\r' :
 
 sb.append("\\r");
 break;
 case '\t' :
 
 sb.append("\\t");
 break;
 case '\\' :
 
 sb.append(backslashEscape);
 break;
 case '\"' :
 
 sb.append(doublequoteEscape);
 break;
 case '\'' :
 
 sb.append(singlequoteEscape);
 break;
 case '>' :
 
 if(i>=2&&((s.charAt(i-1)=='-'&&s.charAt(i-2)=='-')||(s.charAt(i-1)==']'&&s.charAt(i-2)==']'))){
 sb.append("\\>");
 }else {
 sb.append(c);
 }
 break;
 case '<' :
 
  final String END_SCRIPT="/script";
  final String START_COMMENT="!--";
 if(s.regionMatches(true,i+1,END_SCRIPT,0,END_SCRIPT.length())){
 sb.append("<\\");
 }else {
 if(s.regionMatches(false,i+1,START_COMMENT,0,START_COMMENT.length())){
 sb.append("<\\");
 }else {
 sb.append(c);
 }
 }
 break;
 default :
 
 if(outputCharsetEncoder!=null){
 if(outputCharsetEncoder.canEncode(c)){
 sb.append(c);
 }else {
 appendHexJavaScriptRepresentation(sb,c);
 }
 }else {
 if(c>0x1f&&c<=0x7f){
 sb.append(c);
 }else {
 appendHexJavaScriptRepresentation(sb,c);
+}
 }
 }
+if(backslashEscape.startsWith("/")){
+backslashEscape=backslashEscape.substring(1);
 }
 }
 sb.append(quote);
 return sb.toString();

  final String END_SCRIPT="/script";
  final String START_COMMENT="!--";
 if(s.regionMatches(true,i+1,END_SCRIPT,0,END_SCRIPT.length())){
 sb.append("<\\");
 }else {
 if(s.regionMatches(false,i+1,START_COMMENT,0,START_COMMENT.length())){
 sb.append("<\\");
 }else {
 sb.append(c);
 }
 }
 break;
 default :

 if(outputCharsetEncoder.canEncode(c)){
 sb.append(c);
 }else {
 appendHexJavaScriptRepresentation(sb,c);
 }
 }else {
+long startTime=System.currentTimeMillis();
 if(c>0x1f&&c<=0x7f){
 sb.append(c);
 }else {
 appendHexJavaScriptRepresentation(sb,c);
 }
+long endTime=System.currentTimeMillis();
+long totalTime=endTime-startTime;
 }
 }

 sb.append(quote);
